Creating Beautiful Presentations With Remark, Apron, Adirondack, and Descartes  The Story Remark Themes Story offers helper themes for creating beautiful presentations with Remark, using simple Markdown to create slide layouts.
 Apron defines the layouts’ structure and size. Adirondack adds typography, theme colors, and helpful features. Descartes provides element and image positioning and colors.  Story has a design goal of clean, simple Markdown content.
